71\n24|31|75\n22|31|47\n20|31|68\n19|31|45\n17|31|38\n16|31|63\n14|31|20\n1|31|34\n12|31|23\n11|31|42\n0|31|28\n7|30|84\n5|30|83\n39|30|68\n37|30|78\n34|30|103\n31|30|96\n29|30|45\n26|30|70\n23|30|83\n2|30|117\n21|30|70\n18|30|64\n15|30|71\n13|30|22\n10|30|65\n\n\nThis would also avoid the the special treatment of data managers.\n\nWhat do you think @nsoranzo and @mvdbeek","files":null}]}